DataSource.SelectSQLQuery: SELECT NOTES_TERM.NOTE_ID,NOTES_TERM.maxver, mstr.NOTE_NM, mstr.NOTE_STTS_CD FROM (SELECT asn.NOTE_ID NOTE_ID,max(asn.NOTE_VRSN_NBR) maxver FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN asn, NMST_NOTE_MSTR mstr WHERE asn.ENTY_TYPE = 'AVAILTERM' AND asn.ENTY_SYS_ID {0} AND asn.NOTE_ID = mstr.NOTE_ID AND asn.NOTE_VRSN_NBR = (SELECT MAX(NOTE_VRSN_NBR) FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR WHERE NOTE_ID = asn.NOTE_ID AND NOTE_STTS_CD = 'PUBLISHED') AND mstr.NOTE_STTS_CD = 'PUBLISHED'AND asn.note_id NOT IN (SELECT note_id FROM note_domn_assn WHERE enty_type = 'AVAILQUALIFIER') GROUP BY asn.NOTE_ID --HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT(asn.ENTY_SYS_ID)) >={1} ) NOTES_TERM, NMST_NOTE_MSTR MSTR WHERE MSTR.NOTE_ID = NOTES_TERM.NOTE_ID and MSTR.NOTE_NM LIKE UPPER({3}) AND MSTR.NOTE_VRSN_NBR = NOTES_TERM.maxver AND NOTES_TERM.NOTE_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT NOTE_ID FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN WHERE ENTY_SYS_ID = to_char({2}) AND BNFT_DEFN_SYS_ID = {4} AND ENTY_TYPE = 'ATTACHBNFTLINE') AND MSTR.NOTE_STTS_CD = 'PUBLISHED' UNION SELECT DISTINCT N.NOTE_ID, MAX (N.NOTE_VRSN_NBR), N.NOTE_NM, N.NOTE_STTS_CD FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR N, (SELECT DISTINCT D.NOTE_ID FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN D, (SELECT N.NOTE_ID, N.NOTE_NM, MAX (N.NOTE_VRSN_NBR) NOTE_VRSN_NBR FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN D, NMST_NOTE_MSTR N WHERE D.NOTE_ID = N.NOTE_ID AND D.NOTE_VRSN_NBR=N.NOTE_VRSN_NBR AND N.NOTE_NM LIKE UPPER({3}) AND N.NOTE_STTS_CD='PUBLISHED' AND N.LGCY_IND ='N' GROUP BY N.NOTE_ID, N.NOTE_NM ) N WHERE D.NOTE_ID = N.NOTE_ID AND D.NOTE_VRSN_NBR=N.NOTE_VRSN_NBR AND D.ENTY_TYPE ='SYSTEM DOMAIN' MINUS SELECT DISTINCT a.NOTE_ID FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN a, nmst_note_mstr b WHERE a.ENTY_TYPE IN ('AVAILBENEFIT', 'AVAILCOMP', 'AVAILPRODUCT','AVAILQUALIFIER','AVAILTERM','AVAILQUESTION') and b.note_stts_cd='PUBLISHED' and a.note_id=b.note_id and a.note_vrsn_nbr=b.note_vrsn_nbr group by a.NOTE_ID ) D WHERE D.NOTE_ID = N.NOTE_ID AND N.NOTE_STTS_CD='PUBLISHED' AND N.NOTE_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT NOTE_ID FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN WHERE ENTY_SYS_ID = to_char({2}) AND BNFT_DEFN_SYS_ID = {4} AND ENTY_TYPE = 'ATTACHBNFTLINE') GROUP BY N.NOTE_ID, N.NOTE_NM, N.NOTE_STTS_CD

SELECT NOTES_TERM.noteId,NOTES_TERM.maxver, mstr.NOTE_NM, mstr.NOTE_STTS_CD FROM ( select A.NOTE_ID noteId, max(A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR) maxver from NOTE_DOMN_ASSN A, NMST_NOTE_MSTR B, (SELECT asn.NOTE_ID NOTE_ID FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN asn, NMST_NOTE_MSTR mstr WHERE (asn.enty_type IN ('AVAILQUALIFIER')) and asn.NOTE_ID = mstr.NOTE_ID AND asn.NOTE_VRSN_NBR = (SELECT MAX(NOTE_VRSN_NBR) FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR WHERE NOTE_ID = asn.NOTE_ID AND NOTE_STTS_CD = 'PUBLISHED') AND mstr.NOTE_STTS_CD = 'PUBLISHED' GROUP BY asn.NOTE_ID)e where A.NOTE_ID= e.NOTE_ID(+) and e.NOTE_ID is null and enty_type in ('AVAILTERM') and enty_sys_id {0} and B.NOTE_ID = A.NOTE_ID and B.NOTE_VRSN_NBR = A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR and B.NOTE_STTS_CD = 'PUBLISHED' GROUP BY A.NOTE_ID
UNION
select A.NOTE_ID noteId, max(A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR) maxver from NOTE_DOMN_ASSN A, NMST_NOTE_MSTR B, (SELECT asn.NOTE_ID NOTE_ID FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN asn, NMST_NOTE_MSTR mstr WHERE (asn.enty_type IN ('AVAILTERM')) and (asn.enty_sys_id {0}) and asn.NOTE_ID = mstr.NOTE_ID AND asn.NOTE_VRSN_NBR = (SELECT MAX(NOTE_VRSN_NBR) FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR WHERE NOTE_ID = asn.NOTE_ID AND NOTE_STTS_CD = 'PUBLISHED') AND mstr.NOTE_STTS_CD = 'PUBLISHED' GROUP BY asn.NOTE_ID) l where A.NOTE_ID = l.NOTE_ID and enty_type in ('AVAILQUALIFIER') and enty_sys_id {2} and B.NOTE_ID = A.NOTE_ID and B.NOTE_VRSN_NBR = A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR and B.NOTE_STTS_CD = 'PUBLISHED' GROUP BY A.NOTE_ID ) NOTES_TERM, NMST_NOTE_MSTR MSTR, (SELECT DISTINCT NOTE_ID FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN WHERE ENTY_SYS_ID = {3} AND BNFT_DEFN_SYS_ID = {5} AND ENTY_TYPE = 'ATTACHBNFTLINE') k WHERE MSTR.NOTE_ID = NOTES_TERM.noteId and MSTR.NOTE_NM LIKE {4} AND MSTR.NOTE_VRSN_NBR = NOTES_TERM.maxver AND NOTES_TERM.noteId = k.NOTE_ID(+) and k.NOTE_ID is null AND MSTR.NOTE_STTS_CD = 'PUBLISHED'
UNION
SELECT N.NOTE_ID, MAX (N.NOTE_VRSN_NBR), N.NOTE_NM, N.NOTE_STTS_CD FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR N, (SELECT DISTINCT D.NOTE_ID FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN D, (SELECT N.NOTE_ID, N.NOTE_NM, MAX (N.NOTE_VRSN_NBR) NOTE_VRSN_NBR FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN D, NMST_NOTE_MSTR N WHERE D.NOTE_ID = N.NOTE_ID AND D.NOTE_VRSN_NBR=N.NOTE_VRSN_NBR AND N.NOTE_NM LIKE {4} AND N.NOTE_STTS_CD='PUBLISHED' AND N.LGCY_IND ='N' GROUP BY N.NOTE_ID, N.NOTE_NM ) N WHERE D.NOTE_ID = N.NOTE_ID AND D.NOTE_VRSN_NBR=N.NOTE_VRSN_NBR AND D.ENTY_TYPE ='SYSTEM DOMAIN' MINUS
SELECT DISTINCT a.NOTE_ID FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN a, nmst_note_mstr b WHERE a.ENTY_TYPE IN ('AVAILBENEFIT', 'AVAILCOMP', 'AVAILPRODUCT','AVAILQUALIFIER','AVAILTERM','AVAILQUESTION') and b.note_stts_cd='PUBLISHED' and a.note_id=b.note_id and a.note_vrsn_nbr=b.note_vrsn_nbr group by a.NOTE_ID ) D, (SELECT DISTINCT NOTE_ID FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN WHERE ENTY_SYS_ID = {3} AND BNFT_DEFN_SYS_ID = {5} AND ENTY_TYPE = 'ATTACHBNFTLINE') f WHERE D.NOTE_ID = N.NOTE_ID AND N.NOTE_STTS_CD='PUBLISHED' AND N.NOTE_ID = f.NOTE_ID(+) and f.NOTE_ID is null GROUP BY N.NOTE_ID, N.NOTE_NM, N.NOTE_STTS_CD
